Two weeks after a moran married two wives in one day, Kajiado was treated to another event in which three sons of a former MCA wed on the same day. Former Purko MCA Samuel Kipaika's sons exchanged vows with their loved ones in a ceremony attended by hundreds of guests. Tom Mako became an instant sensation after marrying two women - Elizabeth Silamoi (24) and Joyce Tikoyian (23) on December 11. Read: 'He is a hero': Kajiado moran praised for marrying two brides at rare wedding Kipaika's sons - Farrouk, Brian and Oscar - said they decided to hold their weddings on the same day because of the love they have for each other. Also Read: Why more women are marrying two husbands Click here for the latest political news